title: Al Siblani on the Value of 3D Printing in Mass Customisation
text:
Al Siblani on the Value of 3D Printing in Mass Customisation 16 October 2015 Expand EnvisionTEC founder, Al Siblani leads the TCT Show + Personalize 2015 Conference sessions with a keynote presentation on the value of mass customisation, what the 3D printing industry looks like today and what he believes the "next big thing" will be. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
